@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### OMNICHANNEL MODULE - Multi-Channel Communication
### ============================================

### CONVERSATIONS - List Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/conversations?page=1&limit=20&status=open
Authorization: {{token}}

### CONVERSATIONS - Get Conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/conversations/:conversationId
Authorization: {{token}}

### CONVERSATIONS - Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/conversations/:conversationId/messages
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Thank you for contacting us!",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "type": "text"
}

### CHANNELS - List Channels
GET {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/channels
Authorization: {{token}}

### CHANNELS - Create Channel
POST {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/channels
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "whatsapp",
  "name": "Support Channel",
  "credentials": {
    "phoneNumber": "+1-555-0123",
    "accessToken": "token-here"
  },
  "enabled": true
}

### CONTACTS - Create Omnichannel Contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/contacts
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "phone": "+1-555-0123",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "platform": "whatsapp"
}

### TEMPLATES - List Message Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/templates?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### TEMPLATES - Create Template
POST {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/templates
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Welcome Message",
  "content": "Welcome! How can we help you today?",
  "category": "greeting",
  "variables": []
}

### INTEGRATIONS - List Integrations
GET {{baseUrl}}/omnichannel/integrations
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Channels: whatsapp, facebook, instagram, email, telegram
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
